Summary: UFO OVER GLORY PEAK ON TETON PASS, WYOMING
divs: Sighting DetailsWe checked the Web Cams on Teton Pass at about 11:30 p.m., February 18th. The Glory Peak Web Cam showed an oval object in the upper right-hand corner of the picutre, probably visible because of the bright moonlight. We printed the four picture set. The object is visible in the picture, but not quite as obvious as it was on the Web Cam. There were a couple of vehicles on the parking lot. Have you had any reports of -- or explanations for -- this object?
